b1 8.77 fish ha-1, 1\u201330 m) relative to lionfish populations in their native ranges, particularly at sites at depths &gt; 18m (mean = 43.39 \u00b1 13.76 fish ha-1, 18\u201330 m). Drawing on lessons from Belize, we discuss the potential for conservation volunteers to support invasive alien species (IAS) monitoring and control efforts in marine environments.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Anderson, L. G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chapman, Jennifer K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Escontrela, Daniela", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gough, Charlotte L A", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 5", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/562681adac9302ca0d5f59e425de2037", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/05c5392ad58699a62bc4f2c42d7ef128f681f6ebfb98b4c7f7a00e836abf9d77", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/RDXMGQUY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/RDXMGQUY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/98a5a737f4ac5bd111cbbd8a1d207602!/b184409-186528", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.3391/mbi.2017.8.4.14", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages": 